'''[[Shell spider]] silk''' was used to create [[Spider silk armor|armor]] that only experts could spot. Resembling normal clothing, the silk could deflect [[Vibroblade/Legends|vibroblades]] and [[Blaster pistol/Legends|blaster pistols]]. [[Mahwi Lihnn]] wore it.

